replies.body:
Issues during patching can be caused by different things depending on where it actually fails (%). We've written up a nifty [Patching Issues guide](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/202969434-Patching-Issues) that I recommend checking out for really common solutions for issues like this.

Let me know if those steps caused any change for you.
I have go through all solution including those, it still not work and nothing changed.  it allway failed at 34%

In that case, we'll have to dive into your system logs to determine what specifically is causing this. I recommend grabbing a set of logs using our [Hextech Tool](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/224826367), then attach them to a [support ticket.](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new)

Let me know if you have any other questions.
I have go through all solution including those, it still not work and nothing changed.
